# Cloudflare Pages _redirects
#
# This file belongs in the repo that powers projects.sillylittle.tech.
# It redirects the /JetVeil path (and any sub-paths) to the dedicated subdomain.
#
# Cloudflare Pages _redirects syntax:
#   <source>  <destination>  <status>
#
# :splat captures everything after the wildcard so deep links still resolve.

/JetVeil     https://jetveil.sillylittle.tech          301
/JetVeil/*   https://jetveil.sillylittle.tech/:splat   301
